# OFM Premium Agency

## Brand & copy
- Accent: pink `#ff5bb5`, violet `#a855f7`, cyan `#00d4ff` on `#050508`
- Income figures: **gross total** disclaimers — never promise net payout
- User-facing JSON copy: edit all 4 locales (`messages/ru.json`, `uk.json`, `en.json`, `es.json`)

## Motion
- Router: `ofm-animation-mastery` for complex/3D work
- Hero: GSAP only; use `ofm-premium-motion` skill for new animation work
- Framer: `framer-motion-animator` + `animation-designer` for sections/gestures
- 3D: `threejs-*` + `react-three-fiber` when user requests — lazy-load, no 3D on mobile ≤767px
- ScrollTrigger: max 6 instances; no blur tweens; mobile ≤767px lite
- All Framer components: `useReducedMotion()` gate

## Conversion
- Primary CTA → `#contact` → Telegram application API
- Calculator result should bridge to contact form when possible
- Use `ofm-conversion-audit` skill before major UX changes

## Quality
- Prefer minimal diffs; match existing patterns in `components/`
- Run `npm run build` after substantive changes
- Use `ofm-deep-site-audit` skill for full-site analysis requests
- React perf: `vercel-react-best-practices` · UI audit: `web-design-guidelines` · Router: `skill-library`
